column5: Got a chance to get to Jiggy.. I dont dont know what happened to july, like a time warp.. but august is gonna be different!!  Congrats on a monster bass Honey bunny although yesterday i said you had a monster bass and you got all mad at me....
Good to hear from ya fella.  Nice bass,and I mean that.
That's beauty! A really nice bass, Monique. Thanks for the post. Hope to see you both REAL soon! What did you fool that fish with, Monique? And TJ, I need a Jiggy Jiggy hat.
yeah, she does have a nice bass
What a beauty!  The bass aint bad either
Nice fat bass you have there Monique
